  "content_id": "92f100c6-b11f-4cdb-b9f4-b7dbb890fc35",
  "description": "Join an Independent Monitoring Board (IMB) to volunteer to check standards in prisons - find out how to apply",
  "details": {
    "body": "\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>Apply to an Independent Monitoring Board for an application pack.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Independent Monitoring Boards check the day-to-day standards of prisons - each prison has one associated with it.</p>\n\n<p>You don’t need specific qualifications and you get trained.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"how-to-apply\">How to apply</h2>\n\n<p>Contact the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://imb.org.uk/prison-volunteer/prison-volunteer-uk/\">Independent Monitoring Board</a> to volunteer.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Independent Monitoring Board</strong><br>\nTelephone: 020 3334 3265<br>\nMonday to Friday, 9am to 5pm<br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Volunteering usually takes up about 2 or 3 days per month.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"what-happens-after-you-return-the-application-pack\">What happens after you return the application pack</h2>\n\n<p>You’ll be invited to a tour of the prison and then asked to go for an interview.</p>\n\n<p>If successful, checks are done on your background - this is called ‘security clearance’.</p>\n\n<p>The process can take up to 3 months.</p>\n\n",
    "external_related_links": [

    ]
  },
